Description
-----------

Restricst file system access to known .
[PK4](PK4_%28file_format%29 "PK4 (file format)") files.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    fs_restrict [Boolean]

Parameters
----------

-   [Boolean]
    -   0 - Allow the use of custom content.
    -   1 - Block the use of custom content.

