Notes
-----

If this CVar is set to 1 and you are unable to change it from the
[console](Console "Console") then you can put it in the
[autoexec.cfg](CFG_%28file_format%29 "CFG (file format)") file or as a
[startup parameter](Startup_parameters "Startup parameters") .

